$ SQL*Plus: SET LOBPREFETCH
@ set lobprefetch

sa:

  The default value of `lobprefetch` is changed to 16384 when using SQL*Plus's → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus/_command-line/options/fast[command line option `-fast`].

  → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/data-types/lob[LOBs (`clob`, `blob` etc.)]

  → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus/set[`set`]

  → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus
